Review Summary

Features

Operating system

Available with Windows 10 Pro - for a smooth, versatile PC experience.

    Video: Dell Precision 3520 (2017) Product Overview 1:14

    Watch Video

    As sharp as your mind

    Built to perform: New 7th Gen Intel® Core™ i5, i7 and Xeon® processors extract powerful performance from your most demanding professional applications, so you can achieve even more in less time.

    Enhanced memory speeds: Memory speeds of up to 2400MHz boost 3D imaging, rendering, and other memory intensive applications to its maximum potential.

    Robust graphics:     Master any visualization challenge in no time with the new NVIDIA® Quadro® M620 graphics card featuring 2GB of memory.

    Improve productivity with Dell Precision Optimizer

    Free with your Precision workstation, the Dell Precision Optimizer takes the guesswork out of customizing settings and automatically tunes your workstation to run the most popular Independent Software Vendor (ISV) applications at the fastest speeds possible. Featuring centralized management with Microsoft SCCM and KACE, simplified systems management to improve system reliability, detailed analytics and smart notifications to proactively address resource bottlenecks, certified graphics drivers downloads and Radeon ProRender ray-tracing plug-ins to render stunningly photorealistic images ― all in an elegant, new UI.

    Keep your ideas in motion

    Prolonged productivity: The 68Whr 4-cell battery and optional 6-cell 92Whr battery so you can stay productive on the job no matter where you need to be.

    Fit for your lifestyle: Designed with cable docking, the smaller, more compact workstation weighs in at less than 5 pounds. Now you can carry your large projects anywhere.

    Small design. Powerful performance.

    This small mobile workstation packs a powerful punch, with an enhanced new design and three different display options. Having up to a FHD touch display means you can bring your greatest ideas to life. Experience ideal color gamut for all your color-critical projects. If you deal with color-critical work like CAD/CAM, graphic, game or animation design, video editing or media creation, Dell PremierColor can give you the color quality and the fine level of detail you require.

    Your work can count on it

    Independent Software Vendor (ISV) certification: Precision Workstations are tested to ensure the high-performance applications you rely on every day run smoothly. Dell ISV-certifications cover the most popular independent software applications.

    Ports & Slots

    1. Headphone Jack | 2. SIM Card Slot | 3. USB 3.0 | 4. VGA Port | 5. Security Lock | 6. RJ45 Port | 7. HDMI Port | 8. USB 3.0 | 9. Power Adapter Port | 10. USB-C Port | 11. USB 3.0 | 12. Memory Card Reader | 13. Smart Card Reader (Optional)

    Dimensions & Weight

    1. Height: (Front 0.97”/24.55mm) | 2. Width: 14.61”/377.1mm | 3. Depth: 9.94”/252.6mm
    Weight: Starting at 4.79 pounds with a 4-cell battery and HD non-touch panel​

    Resources

    Precision 3520 Specs

    Essential accessories for your Precision 3520

    Maximize your productivity and push your ideas even further with an Ultra HD Monitor and Wireless Premium Keyboard and Mouse.

    Dell 27 Ultra HD Monitor | P2715Q

    Hone in on the fine details and give your work the attention it deserves with four times the resolution of Full HD.

    Dell Premier Wireless Keyboard and Mouse | KM717

    Work comfortably on virtually any surface with an arc-shaped mouse and full-sized keyboard, and easily switch between three devices via Bluetooth LE and Dell Universal Pairing.

    Dell Thunderbolt™ Dock | TB16

    Connect your Precision to a single data and power source for the ultimate display performance (up to three FHD displays or two 4K displays) and faster data transfers. (Requires optional Thunderbolt port.)

    We've got your business covered

    ProSupport Plus

    Get anytime priority access to expert support with predictive analytics (via SupportAssist technology*) and damage protection for drops, spills, surges and more.

    ProDeploy Plus

    This comprehensive service provides seamless deployment of new technology. You get a single point of contact for project management including up-front planning, configuration, data migration and knowledge transfer.

    Accidental Damage Service

    Enjoy worry-free ownership and minimize downtime with protection from accidental drops, spills, surges and breakages. Coverage picks up where your previous warranty leaves off and is ideal for high-risk environments and mobile workforces.
